==Tailoring==
Copper Ore can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Turtleneck Sweater]].  [[File:Shirt178.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*The morning after collecting 1 Copper Ore, [[Clint]] will visit you and give you the blueprints for crafting a [[Furnace]].  This creates the [[Quests#Forging Ahead|"Forging Ahead" quest]].
*[[Clint]] may ask you to collect various numbers of Copper Ore in random [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|Gathering Quests]] at the "Help Wanted" board outside [[Pierre's General Store]].
*10 Copper Ore are requested by [[Stonefish]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 1 to 3.

==History==
